# NaviSphere — Railway Station Resource Tracker
## Complete Project Review Summary

---

## 🧭 What Is This Project?

**NaviSphere** is an **indoor navigation and resource tracking system** for railway stations.
A passenger can open the web app, pick any station, select a **Start** and **End** location (e.g., from the Main Entrance to Platform 4/5), and the system instantly draws the **shortest path** on an interactive station map.

Currently supported stations:
| Station | Platforms |
|---|---|
| Secunderabad Junction | 10 platforms + full facilities |
| Lingampally | 4 platforms |
| Medchal Station | 5 platforms |
| Gadwal Station | 2 platforms |

