## 🏗️ Architecture — How Is the Project Structured?

The project is a **full-stack web application** split into two parts:

```
navisphere/
├── backend/    ← Python + FastAPI (REST API)
└── frontend/   ← React.js (User Interface)
```

### Flow Diagram

```
User (Browser)
    │  selects start + destination
    ▼
React Frontend (Vite + React)
    │  sends POST /navigate via Axios (HTTP)
    ▼
FastAPI Backend (Python + Uvicorn)
    │  runs Dijkstra's algorithm on a graph
    ▼
JSON response: { "path": ["Node A", "Node B", ...] }
    │
    ▼
React-Konva renders the path as a glowing line on
the station blueprint image
```

