## 📡 API Endpoint

```
POST http://localhost:8000/navigate
```

**Request Body:**
```json
{
  "station_name": "Secunderabad Junction",
  "start": "Main Entrance",
  "destination": "Platform 4/5"
}
```

**Response:**
```json
{
  "path": [
    "Main Entrance",
    "Ticket Counter",
    "WP_PF10_Stairs_FOB1",
    "WP_PF89_Stairs_FOB1",
    "WP_PF67_Stairs_FOB1",
    "FOB 1 (Foot Over Bridge)",
    "WP_PF45_Stairs_FOB1",
    "Platform 4/5"
  ]
}
```

